Otyebis Staff/Sinew:



The skimmer that held the Autobots lightly rocked from the missiles striking 
its shields.  The cannons of the Otyebis were ready to fire, but didn't.  A 
small hatch opened up in the side of one of the skimmers, a large robot whose 
origin is not of Cybertron flying out and through the shields unharmed.

The twelve foot robot raised its massive arms, two tips that were the 
beginning of missiles beginning to appear from his hand.

"Leave this area now or be destroyed."
